00:33:38.459 --> 00:33:43.259
Let's pray. Father, we love you. We thank you for loving us. We thank you for the privilege

00:33:43.259 --> 00:33:47.839
that you've given for us to gather this evening. We thank you for the freedom. We thank you

00:33:47.839 --> 00:33:53.459
God for your word. And Lord, how thankful we are that we have a Bible. And Lord, we

00:33:53.459 --> 00:33:58.759
can see the purpose here in the psalm with regard to the children of Israel and the feast

00:33:58.759 --> 00:34:03.359
of tabernacles. But then as we seek to make application tonight, Lord, would you help

00:34:03.359 --> 00:34:09.839
us to be mindful to remember the deliverance that we have. The fact that we've been saved

00:34:09.839 --> 00:34:19.199
by your grace. Lord, help us to live every day with a level of gratitude and great appreciation

00:34:19.199 --> 00:34:26.720
for what you've done for us. That we're heaven bound. So thankful that one day I'll see you

00:34:26.720 --> 00:34:31.599
face to face. Lord, I pray that you would bless our time of prayer. We thank you for

00:34:31.599 --> 00:34:35.440
the privilege. We thank you that you're God who hears and answers. I pray that you'd be

00:34:35.440 --> 00:34:47.639
honored and glorified and we'll thank you for it in Christ's name we pray. Amen.

